    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What can you expect?</h2><br>We affectionately call it &quot;queer cheesy trash&quot;. The 90s FMVs had their own charm and that included exaggerated acting, exaggerated characters and a penchant for hoarding items. We want to get back to that.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100% FMV Point and Click Adventure Game<br></li><li> 2 alternating playable main characters<br></li><li> 15 different playable locations in Austria<br></li><li> 13 interactive NPCs<br></li><li> classic point and click puzzles!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>Markus was recently a pretty normal average guy. He has no particular ambitions in life and keeps his head above water as a photographer of photo books of questionable quality. But when he is plagued by nightmares, he starts to investigate. And a letter addressed to him, but with the wrong surname, changes his life completely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/e8293101279d83624995e3fa8cdb9099.poster.avif?t=1701513922\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/e8293101279d83624995e3fa8cdb9099.webm?t=1701513922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/e8293101279d83624995e3fa8cdb9099.mp4?t=1701513922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The blood of a time-honored family of Shadowhunters beats in his heart. And with it comes a responsibility to his fellow man. For the Shadowhunters are destined to fight demonic beings, so-called 'shadows'. One such monster is currently killing in Vienna and has already claimed countless victims. Will Markus be up to the task?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/312cb2ef68cf09d61e84d8d4cb733751.poster.avif?t=1701513922\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/312cb2ef68cf09d61e84d8d4cb733751.webm?t=1701513922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/312cb2ef68cf09d61e84d8d4cb733751.mp4?t=1701513922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But not only the supernatural plagues our young Shadowhunter. His publisher has big plans for a book that Markus himself hasn't even written. Will his presence in the public eye be advantageous, or will it hinder his existence as a Shadowhunter?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/e30c6b7d88d802a0be2dfb85ae00613f.poster.avif?t=1701513922\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/e30c6b7d88d802a0be2dfb85ae00613f.webm?t=1701513922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222680/extras/e30c6b7d88d802a0be2dfb85ae00613f.mp4?t=1701513922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Then there's also his love life, which takes off at a most inconvenient time. There's Claudia, the secretary, but also Ludwig, the charismatic digital designer.<br><br>And then there's Ro. A young woman who suddenly appears everywhere the shadow is. What's the story behind her?",
